&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/pillipillihandmade/4757203416/" title="all set for small accidents..."&gt;&lt;img src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4100/4757203416_ebbc066219_m.jpg" width="240" height="240" alt="all set for small accidents..." /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Those of you who have children&lt;br /&gt;
(or who, like me, have a slight tendency&lt;br /&gt;
to walk with their head in the clouds)&lt;br /&gt;
know that small accidents happen!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
SO BE PREPARED!    :o)&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
*&lt;br /&gt;
This sweet linen pouch is nice and small, so can go anywhere with you; on a hiking trip, to the park, the beach... yet it's just big enough to hold all the essentials to cure small accidents! Bandaids, some aspirine, your allergy tablets, an asthma inhaler, a pair of scissors, an extra few tampons, a small bottle of disinfectant...&lt;/p&gt;

