&lt;p&gt;...but when you are talking about a large (+10K lbs) trailer like this, getting there is also serious business. Thankfully, we have Richard &amp;quot;Dick&amp;quot; Burrows, a professional defensive driving instructor for truck drivers, who is volunteering his time to help the Greater Ozarks Chapter make sure that we have qualified drivers to get &lt;a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/ozarksredcross/5097797881/"&gt;this rig&lt;/a&gt; where it needs to be during the next disaster response in the Missouri Ozarks. (Photo by Perry, Red Cross Volunteer)&lt;/p&gt;

